    trt:citesTaxonName <http://taxon-name.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Halicornaria>, <http://taxon-name.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Halicornaria_allmani>, <http://taxon-name.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Gymnagium_allmani>, <http://taxon-name.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Gymnangium_longicauda>, <http://taxon-name.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Halicornaria_pennatula> ;
